Class OpenAtMethodAction

java.lang.Object
  com.rohanclan.cfml.editors.actions.OpenAtMethodAction
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.ui.IActionDelegate, org.eclipse.ui.IEditorActionDelegate
public class OpenAtMethodAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.eclipse.ui.IEditorActionDelegate

Author:
Rob This action causes a file to be opened in the editor. The file can either be a string-based path relative to the workspace root, or an IFile. The file will be opened with whatever editor is associated with the file type.
